<item>
            <title>[LU-15381] Obtain file size information under locks for HSM release</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15381</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In HSM release, it obtains file size and blocks information via @ll_merge_attr without any lock protection, it may get the wrong file size.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;we found a bug that a HSM restore followed by a HSM release will set the file size with 0 wrongly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
