                            <comment id="321093" author="qian_wc" created="Fri, 17 Dec 2021 08:01:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As we use data version to flush all cache and revoke the locks on all clients, thus we could update the size and block attributes in data version operations (however, it still does not protect with any locks)?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By this way, we can avoid the glimpse RPC to get the file size?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Will make a patch sooner.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
